Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 10 of Head MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Pathology' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Pathology' is selected in the dropdown menu

When I click on 'Add new finding' button
Then a new dropdown menu is added and is active
And 'Add new finding' button is disabled
